{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id44b09fae-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s1053"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1053"},"text":"§ 1053.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Property acquired before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-03-01"},"text":"March 1, 1913","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of property acquired before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-03-01"},"text":"March 1, 1913","children":[],"tail":", if the basis otherwise determined under this subtitle, adjusted (for the period before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-03-01"},"text":"March 1, 1913","children":[],"tail":") as provided in section 1016, is less than the fair market value of the property as of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-03-01"},"text":"March 1, 1913","children":[],"tail":", then the basis for determining gain shall be such fair market value. In determining the fair market value of stock in a corporation as of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-03-01"},"text":"March 1, 1913","children":[],"tail":", due regard shall be given to the fair market value of the assets of the corporation as of that date."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id44b09faf-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736"},"text":"Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68A/311"},"text":"68A Stat. 311","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/866/tI/s47"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–866, title I, § 47","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-09-02"},"text":"Sept. 2, 1958","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/72/1642"},"text":"72 Stat. 1642","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"